high_descs: Walk ahead to the counter and then right all the way to the left side of the other counter ahead of you.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Look down at the counter.
Place the knife black cup closest to the side of the counter.
Pick up the black cup.
Turn right and veer left to the sink.
Place the cup in the sink to the left of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a knife in it in a sink.

high_descs: Walk across the room, then turn right and walk to the edge of the counter ahead, then turn right to face it.
Pick up the knife that is to the left of the green sponge on the counter.
Look down at the counter.
Put the knife in the black cup closest to the bottom edge of the counter.
Pick up the cup with the knife in it.
Turn right and walk to the fridge, then turn left and walk across the room to the sink.
Place the cup with the knife in it in the left side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To move the dishes to the sink.

high_descs: Cross the room, hang a right at the counter, and turn right just before the door to face the counter.
Pick up the knife to the left of the green sponge on the counter.
Look down at the counter top towards the black glasses.
Put the knife inside the black glass closest to the light switch.
Pick up the glass with the knife inside.
Turn right, hang a left at the fridge and cross the room to the sink.
Put the knife and the glass inside the sink to the left of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass with a knife in a sink.
